title: Rookies - Series 1
content:
Here is the full first series of my SCP animated sketch comedy Rookies.

Credits for individual episodes can be found at my [https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/art:animated-series-rookies-fifty3dragons animation hub].

Many thanks for all the wonderful support so far. Lots more to come!
